		<hr size="1">My best guess is that it was a bit of both. For holding aggro, I personally suggest Frostbringer in primary and Venomous Axe of the Velium Brood in secondary. They both proc a DD spell, and those procs help a lot in holding aggro, plus the extra damage is always nice. Lay down the law in groups, don't let them tank, or settle with not being the main tank in a group. Just my two cents. (by the way, I don't think they proc until 35... I could be wrong, if anyone could clarify this for me, please do)</P><P><BR>[Magelos coming soon]<BR>Quellious<BR>Daikat - 16 Warrior<BR>Sylph Kerridwen - 25 Mage<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
