		<hr size="1">  The sit taunt has one huge problem and the reason I dont use it.  When the mob returns to you, you have to get up before he gets to you or you get caught in a sit-stand cycle.  The mob hits you, so you auto stand at the same time you hit the stand button, the result you sit and take another hit for full damage.  Sit taunt can and most of the time is a fast trip to bind.  One more little thing all mobs react different to sit some just dont care.  Also bows are great to use with a fd puller, I like em to fd in back of me.</P><P>Rodney<BR>Overlord CT<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
